column2: HONG LEONG FINANCE NOMINEES PTE LTD
LEE KIM TIONG @ LEE KIM YEW
CHNG ENG KEONG OR MICHELLE HO PUAY HOON
BASED ON THE INFORMATION AVAILABLE TO THE COMPANY AS AT 5 DECEMBER 2018, BEING THE LATEST PRACTICABLE DATE, APPROXIMATELY 46.04%
OF THE ISSUED ORDINARY SHARES OF THE COMPANY ARE HELD BY THE PUBLIC. ACCORDINGLY THE COMPANY HAS COMPLIED WITH RULE 723 OF THE
LISTING MANUAL SECTION B: RULES OF THE CATALIST OF THE SINGAPORE EXCHANGE SECURITIES TRADING LIMITED AND RULE 8.08 OF THE RULES
GOVERNING THE LISTING OF SECURITIES ON THE STOCK EXCHANGE OF HONG KONG LIMITED.
